edu.umass.cs.gnsclient.examples

Class ClientExample

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umass.cs.gnsclient.examples.ClientExample

  • public class ClientExample
extends Object
    In this example we create an account to write and read back JSON Objects to the GNS.

    Note: This example cheats during account guid creation in that it creates the account guid and then uses the known secret to verify the account instead of making the user verify the account manually deal with the private key.
